<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702985>
    bibo:endPage "21" ;
    bibo:issue "753" ;
    bibo:journal "Insecta Mundi" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2020-02-28" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    dc:creator "Brown, John W.; Razowski, Józef; Timm, Alicia E." ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Revision of New World Cosmorrhyncha Meyrick, 1913 (Lepidoptera: Tortricidae: Olethreutinae), with descriptions of five new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702995>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702987>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702997> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702995>
    dc:description "Figures 22–26. Female genitalia of Cosmorrhyncha. 22) C. tonsana from Brazil, USNM slide 145,538.23) C.ocelliferana from Brazil, USNM slide 124,775. 24) C. macrospina from Brazil, USNM slide 126,236. 25) C. albistrigulana from Guatemala, USNM slide 124,801. 26) C. osana from Costa Rica, USNM slide 142,202." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3702995/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702987>
    dc:description "Figures 1–3. Neighbor-joining trees. 1) Tree based on all available sequences of Cosmorrhyncha (n = 28), regardless of sequence length. 2) Tree based on sequences excluding the the 200bp segment that could not be amplified for several specimens of Cosmorrhyncha (n = 24). 3) Tree based on all sequences longer than 500bp (n = 23). [Bootstrap values ≥70 shown at nodes; BOLD process IDs or GenBank accession numbers next to species names.]" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3702987/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3702997>
    dc:description "Figures 27–30. Early stages of Cosmorrhyncha in Costa Rica. 27) Rolled leaf shelter of C. tonsana. 28) Larva of C. albistrigulana emerging to feed from leaf roll. 29) Last instar larva of C. tonsana. 30) Pupa of C. tonsana." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3702997/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

